AddressInfo.Title: LMT Inc.
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Provided as a service to promote EV adoption in the area. LMT is located East of the center of Galva, IL on US Hwy 34. Across the highway from the ethanol plant. The charger is located on the North side of the building to the left of the main entrance.

GeneralComments: JuiceBox Pro 40 Smart EV Charging Station with WiFi - 40 amp Level 2 EVSE, 24-foot cable. Powered by 150 x 345W (50kW) Solar Panel Array - WiFi SSID: LMT_Guest  And no, the sun does not need to be shining.
